{"tid":1537522,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2/9 食Jollibee讀何蔭棠果個妹妹請入","createTime":"2019-09-04T03:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T03:16:07.000Z","uid":232228,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"68169ab6e6072976d00a92e59d8ce8417717ef9e","tid":1537522,"uid":232228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:04:58.000Z","msg":"借朋友AC開, 妹妹你好, 我就係2/9係Jollibee坐你隔離枱2個叔叔其中一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇到你地開學禮上面所展現既決心同團結, 我好感動, 男人老狗都眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只希望你地可以堅持, 無論對咩事都好, 只要係自己認為應該做既事, 就去做左先, 年輕既好處就係唔怕行錯路(更何況你地冇做錯)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你思路好清晰, 轉數又快, 口齒伶俐, 將來一定會有一番成就<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記住要罷課不罷學, 不罷休, 要做未來社會既上流, 無忘初心, 先可以改變呢個社會, 往後既人生加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好好似我咁讀唔成書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我願意做支撐棟樑既地底泥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比較之下我果間母校垃圾到仆街, 打壓學生表達...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n保良局何蔭棠中學同學們好波！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536985\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536985</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"b48016c89ae8363dca9cd8098959379ad92f81c7","tid":1537522,"uid":232228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:05:10.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"db9c10d5e86b6b3d9a0201a025add16636719eef","tid":1537522,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:05:17.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75925a8238b4c6e35bc401501815937b8fe494ee","tid":1537522,"uid":232228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:05:21.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"3b5be5110445a448b58f9b2a1704f7781701c5c1","tid":1537522,"uid":232228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:05:36.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"ed7d9cf3e30ac9a83d87987423371412517de4ae","tid":1537522,"uid":232228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:05:54.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"aa6ed43ce78213c06ab4bf5fa83b16696d4214ce","tid":1537522,"uid":232228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:06:04.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"2d71e5ee384ffbe28c56fb5e3b94aa86939be732","tid":1537522,"uid":232228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:06:14.000Z","msg":"721 831"},{"pid":"3599f3e3917e40c765837dcbe3552766b19cb8a8","tid":1537522,